Ajay Devgn]] in his second directorial film ''[[Shivaay]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/screen/sayesha-saigal-to-debut-in-ajay-devgns-shivay/|title=Sayyeshaa to debut in Ajay Devgn's Shivay|date=24 October 2014|accessdate=6 November 2015|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151119164549/http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/screen/sayesha-saigal-to-debut-in-ajay-devgns-shivay/|archivedate=19 November 2015|df=dmy-all}}</ref> Her movie ''[[Vanamagan]]'' hit the theatres in June 2017, marking her [[Tamil language|Tamil]] debut.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.deccanchronicle.com/entertainment/kollywood/180617/sayyeshaa-upbeat-about-vanamagan.html|title=Sayyeshaa upbeat about Vanamagan|last=|first=|date=2017-06-18|work=www.deccanchronicle.com/|access-date=2017-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170619113116/http://www.deccanchronicle.com/entertainment/kollywood/180617/sayyeshaa-upbeat-about-vanamagan.html|archive-date=19 June 2017|url-status=live|language=en|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.top10cinema.com/article/42463/vanamagan-release-postponed-due-to-kollywood-strike|title=Vanamagan release postponed due to Kollywood strike|date=2017-05-10|work=Top 10 Cinema|access-date=2017-06-20|language=en-US|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170821085015/https://www.top10cinema.com/article/42463/vanamagan-release-postponed-due-to-kollywood-strike|archivedate=21 August 2017|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.filmibeat.com/tamil/movies/vanamagan.html|title=Vanamagan Tamil Movie, Wiki, Story, Review, Release Date, Trailers - Filmibeat|website=FilmiBeat|access-date=2017-06-20|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170624142349/http://www.filmibeat.com/tamil/movies/vanamagan.html|archivedate=24 June 2017|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.celebhdwall.in/2016/05/sayesha-saigal-wiki-biography-age.html|title=Sayyeshaa Ta