ation. In 2005, Saturn started a videoblog, ZipZapZop.com as well as MyGermanClass.com.\n\n==Trivia==\nClark ov Saturn is left-handed.\nClark had a son, Rishi, born on April 3, 2007. A Socks and Sandals EP on Microcosm Music was named for him, Rishi Saturn.\n\n==References==\n{{refbegin}}\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{refend}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.clarksaturn.com] - Clark ov Saturn's homepage.\n*{{IMDb name|1886637}}\n*[http://spacetruckingmogul.com/socksandsandals/] Socks and Sandals homepage\n*[http://microcosm-music.com/socksandsandals.html] Socks and Sandals on Microcosm-Music\n*[http://mygermanclass.com] MyGermanClass.com\n*[http://zipzapzop.com] ZipZapZop.com\n\n==Articles==\n*[http://spacetruckingmogul.com/articles/aurelia.html] Aurelia Star newspaper article\n*[http://www.westword.com/1996-12-19/news/sprechen-sie-interactive] Denver Westword Article\n*''New York Times'': [https://www.nytimes.com/2005/05/22/nyregion/thecity/22weat.html \"Weatherperson Wanted. Bring Own Map. And Jokes. \"]\n*''Denver Westword'': [http://www.westword.com/2001-03-29/calendar/best-career-upgrade-by-a-former-local] \"Best Career Upgrade by a Former Local\"\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Saturn, Clark}}\n[[Category:American filmmakers]]\n[[Category:21st-century American comedians]]\n[[Category:People from Cedar Falls, Iowa]]\n[[Category:American electronic musicians]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:American male television actors]]\n[[Category:American DJs]]\n[[Category:1969 births]]\n[[Category:Luther College (Iowa) alumni]]\n[[Category:Electronic dance music DJs]]\n", "name_user": "Alistair1978", "label": "safe", "comment": "typo (viaWP:JWB)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clark_Saturn"}
{"title_page": "Steinar \u00de\u00f3r Gu\u00f0geirsson", "text_new": "{{short description|Icelandic footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name= Steinar \u00de\u00f3r Gu\u00f0geirsson\n| image = \n| fullname = \n| birth_date  = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1971|8|19}}\n| birth_place = \n| position = defender\n| youthyears1= \n| youthclubs1= \n| years1 = 1989\u20131992\n| clubs1 = [[Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 Fram|Fram]]\n| years2 = 1992\u20131993\n| clubs2 = KFC Heultje\n| years3 = 1993\u20131997\n| clubs3 = [[Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 Fram|Fram]]\n| years4 = 1998\n| clubs4 = [[\u00cd\u00fer\u00f3ttabandalag Vestmannaeyja|\u00cdB Vestmannaeyja]]\n| years5 = 1999\u20132000\n| clubs5 = [[Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 Fram|Fram]]\n| manageryears1  = 2013\n| managerclubs1  = [[Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 Fram|Fram]]\n| nationalyears1 = 1991\n| nationalteam1  = [[Iceland national football team|Iceland]]\n| nationalcaps1  = 1\n| nationalgoals1 = 0\n}}\n\n'''Steinar \u00de\u00f3r Gu\u00f0geirsson''' (born 19 August 1971) is a retired [[Iceland|Icelandic]] [[football midfielder]].<ref>[https://www.weltfussball.de/spieler_profil/steinar-thor-gudgeirsson/ Weltfussball]</ref><ref>{{NFT player|62137}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Gudgeirsson, Steinar Thor}}\n[[Category:1971 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Icelandic footballers|Steinar Thor Gudgeirsson]]\n[[Category:Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 Fram players|Einar Pall Tomasson]]\n[[Category:\u00cd\u00fer\u00f3ttabandalag Vestmannaeyja players|Einar Pall Tomasson]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Icelandic expatriate footballers|Steinar Thor Gudgeirsson]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Belgium]]\n[[Category:Icelandic expatriate sportspeople in Belgium|Steinar Thor Gudgeirsson]]\n[[Category:Iceland international footballers|Steinar Thor Gudgeirsson]]\n[[Category:Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 Fram managers|Einar Pall Tomasson]]\n\n{{Iceland-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Icelandic footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name= Steinar \u00de\u00f3r Gu\u00f0geirsson\n| image = \n| fullname = \n| birth_date  = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1971|8|19}}\n| birth_place = \n| position = defender\n| youthyears1= \n| youthclubs1= \n| years1 = 1989\u20131992\n| clubs1 = [[Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 Fram|Fram]]\n| years2 = 1992\u20131993\n| clubs2 = KFC Heultje\n| years3 = 1993\u20131997\n| clubs3 = [[Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 Fram|Fram]]\n| years4 = 1998\n| clubs4 = [[\u00cd\u00fer\u00f3ttabandalag Vestmannaeyja|\u00cdB Vestmannaeyja]]\n| years5 = 1999\u20132000\n| clubs5 = [[Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 Fram|Fram]]\n| manageryears1  = 2013\n| managerclubs1  = [[Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 Fram|Fram]]\n| nationalyears1 = 1991\n| nationalteam1  = [[Iceland national football team|Iceland]]\n| nationalcaps1  = 1\n| nationalgoals1 = 0\n}}\n\n'''Steinar \u00de\u00f3r Gu\u00f0geirsson''' (born 19 August 1971) is a retired [[Iceland|Icelandic]] [[football midfielder]].<ref>[https://www.weltfussball.de/spieler_profil/steinar-thor-gudgeirsson/ Weltfussball]</ref><ref>{{NFT player|62132}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Gudgeirsson, Steinar Thor}}\n[[Category:1971 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Icelandic footballers|Steinar Thor Gudgeirsson]]\n[[Category:Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 Fram players|Einar Pall Tomasson]]\n[[Category:\u00cd\u00fer\u00f3ttabandalag Vestmannaeyja players|Einar Pall Tomasson]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Icelandic expatriate footballers|Steinar Thor Gudgeirsson]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Belgium]]\n[[Category:Icelandic expatriate sportspeople in Belgium|Steinar Thor Gudgeirsson]]\n[[Category:Iceland international footballers|Steinar Thor Gudgeirsson]]\n[[Category:Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 Fram managers|Einar Pall Tomasson]]\n\n{{Iceland-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Geschichte", 